Package: cryptocompareR
Title: Cryptocompare Api in R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Beniamino Sartini
Maintainer: Beniamino Sartini <sartinibeniamino@gmail.com>
Description: A wrapper for different informations regarding the cypto market, such as 'OHLCV' time series, social data, exchange data and more. 
             The package provide a way to comunicate with the Cryptocompare Api and to retrieve the outputs in a standard and 'tidy' format.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    lubridate,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    httr
Imports:
    jsonlite, 
    magrittr,
    stringr,
    tibble,
    tidyr (>= 1.0.0),
Suggests:
    tidyverse,
    broom,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0),
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
